Description: Prolog is a logic programming language associated with artificial intelligence and computational linguistics

Program 1: Design a simple database in Prolog using constants and variables and execute queries. 

Code: 
% Constants (facts)
likes(john, pizza).
likes(mary, sushi).
likes(jane, pizza).
likes(jane, sushi).
% Variables (rules)
likes_both(X,Y,Z) :- likes(X,Z), likes(Y,Z).
likes_pizza(X) :- likes(X,pizza).

Queries: 
likes(john, pizza). 
likes(jane, burger). 
likes_both(john, mary, pizza). 
likes_pizza(X). 
